11 improvements that is excluded based on the taxable year:
12 Year Percent of Appraised Value Excluded
13 Year 1 90%
14 Year 2 75%
15 Year 3 50%
16 Year 4 30%
17 Year 5 10%."
18 SECTION 4.(c) Subsection (a) of this section becomes effective January 1, 2026.
19 Subsection (b) of this section is effective for taxes imposed for taxable years beginning on or
20 after July 1, 2025.
