25 EXPAND ELIGIBILITY FOR TARGETED INTEREST RATES ON WATER AND
26 WASTEWATER PROJECTS
27 SECTION 6. G.S. 159G-20(21) reads as rewritten:
28 "(21) Targeted interest rate project. – Either of the following types of projects:
29 a. A project that is awarded a loan from the Drinking Water Reserve or
30 the Wastewater Reserve based on affordability.
31 b. A project that is awarded a loan from the CWSRF or the DWSRF and
32 is in a category for which the Department or federal law encourages a
33 special focus."
